          "comment_text": {
            "matchLevel": "none",
            "matchedWords": [],
            "value": "Solution!\nLike everyone else, I updated Codex, it deleted itself and the download appeared to be the installer for the old ChatGPT.  However...  Quit (the old) ChatGPT, then install from this new installer.\nThen ChatGPT Codex opens, WITH all your conversations from the old Codex... as well as your conversations with the old ChatGPT (under the &quot;Chat&quot; option)."
